nodes.text: Nien Nunb, Kessel Administrator: An Expanded Universe Character

Nien Nunb, Kessel Administrator: An Expanded Universe Character is an article on the Wizards of the Coast website written by Cory J. Herndon. It details the career of the Sullustan pilot Nien Nunb, and provided his roleplaying statistics.
